### Read all Books (OData V2)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Books
Accept: application/json

### Read Books with Author expanded (OData V2)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Books?$expand=author
Accept: application/json

### Create a new Book (OData V2)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Rich Dad Poor Dad",
  "stock": 100,
  "price": "19.99",
  "author_ID": "f93548bd-032f-4ddd-a37c-269085dd6c7d"
}

### Read all Authors (OData V2)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Authors
Accept: application/json

### Create a new Author (OData V2)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Robert Kiyosaki",
  "country": "USA"
}


### Get all Notifications (OData V2)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Notifications
Accept: application/json

### Create a manual Notification
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Notification",
  "message": "This is a test notification message",
  "type": "info",
  "priority": "normal",
  "isRead": false
}

### Mark Notification as read (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/Notifications('a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a5b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isRead": true
}
### Get unread notification count (Custom function)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v2/study/getUnreadNotificationCount
Accept: application/json